title: Lila (Mantis In Lace)
description:
LILA (Mantis in Lace)
1968

MPEG-4 Nero Digital
Audio AAC

Psychedelic strip club sex murders

The sweetest lil ol cupcake you ever saw becomes a MANTIS -- she mates, and then she kills.

Police investigate.

Directed by William Rotsler
Cinematography by Laszlo Kovacs (Academy Award Winner)

Music by ? -- they do a cover version of Love's "Can't Explain" -- L.A. baby!

Warmly recommended but come to it with the lowest expectations please. Let it please you as it may, within its modest capabilities. It's beautifully photographed, the trippy effects are OK and the MANTIS is a delightful creature.
